Scovile scale (SHU) 
[https://scovillescale.org/chili-pepper-scoville-scale/]
<scovileScale> ->

    1\-2 Mild (0 \- 2 000 SHU),
    3\-6 Mild Hot (2K \- 50K SHU),
    7\-8 Hot (50K+ SHU),
    9 Spicy Hot (100K+),
    10 Very Hot (250K+),
    10+ Really Hot (500K+),
    10++ Fiery Hot (1M+),
    10+++ Extremely Hot (1.5M+);